title: Double Garlic-Herb Beef & Creamy Pesto Salad  with Feta & Toasted Almonds | Top Rated
description: Quickly-cooked beef strips meld together wonderfully with creamy basil pesto dressing in this Mediterranean-style salad. Make it
a meal with crumbly Greek-style cheese, and now you’ve got yourself a fusion of textures and flavours you simply can’t miss out on!
